{"arkId":"cl010110052","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010110052","modified ":"2025-10-31","title":"N\u00e9cessaire de voyage","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"N\u00e9cessaire de voyage"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Premier Empire (1804-1814) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque contemporaine)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1805 - 1809","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1805,"endYear":1809,"imprecision":"","text":"1e quart du XIXe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Biennais, Martin-Guillaume","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1764","place":"Coch\u00e8re (La)","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1843","place":"Paris","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Orf\u00e8vre","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q1694164"},{"label":"Genu, Marie-Joseph-Gabriel","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"vers 1763","place":"Paris","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1810","place":"Paris","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q28122270"},{"label":"Naudin, Fran\u00e7ois-Dominique","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"23\/12\/1778","place":"Les Andelys (Eure)","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"03\/01\/1841","place":"Paris","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q20656156"},{"label":"Dallemagne, Charles-Joachim-Benjamin","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"14\/06\/1759","place":"Paris","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"11\/11\/1821","place":"Paris","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""},{"label":"Devicque, Gabriel-Joachim","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"29\/03\/1800","place":"Paris","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 9698","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"accessoire personnel, bo\u00eete, \u00e9tui ; n\u00e9cessaire","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Le coffre, bord\u00e9 d\u2019une frise de laurier le long de ses ar\u00eates, est richement orn\u00e9 de sphinges adoss\u00e9es sur le couvercle \u2013 motif que l\u2019on retrouve sur le n\u00e9cessaire du tsar Alexandre (OA 10359), d\u2019hippocampes, de vases, de cornes d\u2019abondance, de palmettes et de fleurons, sur la face et les c\u00f4t\u00e9s. La tranche est \u00e9galement incrust\u00e9e d\u2019une frise de losanges et de fleurons. Ce coffret est du type que Biennais appelle en \u00ab acajou creus\u00e9 \u00bb, c\u2019est-\u00e0-dire qu\u2019il n\u2019est pas garni et compartiment\u00e9 en maroquin ; ces n\u00e9cessaires sont les plus luxueux. Celui-ci ne contient ni bassin \u00e0 barbe, ni rasoirs ou blaireaux, il s\u2019agit donc plut\u00f4t d\u2019un objet f\u00e9minin.\r\nCe n\u00e9cessaire comprend un service \u00e0 th\u00e9 et \u00e0 caf\u00e9 pour deux personnes : une th\u00e9i\u00e8re ovale et sa passoire, une cafeti\u00e8re cylindrique \u00e0 manche en \u00e9b\u00e8ne, un pot \u00e0 cr\u00e8me, des bo\u00eetes \u00e0 th\u00e9 et \u00e0 caf\u00e9, deux couteaux, deux couverts, deux cuillers \u00e0 caf\u00e9, deux tasses et leurs soucoupes. Un miroir, fix\u00e9 au volet int\u00e9rieur du couvercle, une brosse \u00e0 dents, des flacons, des ustensiles \u00e0 manche de nacre pour l\u2019hygi\u00e8ne dentaire, des ciseaux et un cure-oreille sont les accessoires destin\u00e9s \u00e0 la toilette. Pour l\u2019\u00e9criture, outre un compas, un porte-plume et des ciseaux, le n\u00e9cessaire dissimule des portefeuilles en maroquin derri\u00e8re un volet de bois dans le couvercle, et une \u00e9critoire dans un tiroir lat\u00e9ral. \r\nUne paire de bo\u00eetes de toilette et la bo\u00eete \u00e0 th\u00e9 portent le poin\u00e7on de Marie-Joseph-Gabriel Genu.\r\nChiffre : PB et couronne de marquis (sur le couvercle).","inscriptions":"Signature : \r ; Biennais orf\u00e8vre de LL. MM. Imp\u00e9riales et Royales \u00e0 Paris","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Profondeur","value":"26,2","displayDimension":"26,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"40,7","displayDimension":"40,7 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Hauteur","value":"15,8","displayDimension":"15,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : acajou\r\nMat\u00e9riau : vermeil = argent dor\u00e9\r\nMat\u00e9riau : \u00e9b\u00e8ne\r\nMat\u00e9riau : cristal\r\nMat\u00e9riau : acier\r\nMat\u00e9riau : ivoire = dent\r\nMat\u00e9riau : or","placeOfCreation":"Paris (France-\u003EIle-de-France = Ile de France)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection Louis-Victor Puiforcat; sa vente, Paris, Drouot, 7 et 8 d\u00e9cembre 1955, lot 111, pl. XXXVII; donation Stavros S. Niarchos, 1955.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Puiforcat-Tabouret, Louis-Victor","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"},{"value":"M. Niarchos, Stavros","note":"","role":", Collectionneur ; Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"donation sous r\u00e9serve d\u0027usu